OL,3,CFuneral announced for teenager who
OL,4,Cdied at holiday park
OL,6,FThe family of a Sheffield teenager who
OL,7,Fdied at an East Yorkshire holiday park
OL,8,Fhave announced details of her funeral.
OL,10,FCherish Bean, 15, and her boyfriend
OL,11,FEthan Slater, 17, were found dead in a
OL,12,Fcabin at Little Eden Holiday Park in
OL,13,FBridlington last month.
OL,15,FThe opening of an inquest at Hull
OL,16,FCoroner's Court on Tuesday heard their
OL,17,Fdeaths were suspected to have been
OL,18,Fcaused by carbon monoxide poisoning.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
