OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1773349952
OL,3,CFuneral announced for teenager who
OL,4,Cdied at holiday park
OL,6,FIn a post on facebook, Cherish's
OL,7,Ffamily announced her funeral would
OL,8,Ftake place at Ecclesfield Church in
OL,9,FSheffield on 26 March. The funeral
OL,10,Fprocession will start at about 11.30am.
OL,12,FIn the post her mother, Devon Andrews,
OL,13,Fsaid: "The pain we are feeling after
OL,14,Flosing Cherish is far beyond anything
OL,15,Fany parents should have to deal with."
OL,17,FShe invited people to line the streets
OL,18,Falong the procession route and wear
OL,19,Fpink, adding: "Anything over the top
OL,20,Fwould be loved by my Cherish".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
